Richemont Says Its Full-Year Operating Profit Jumps 63% as Sales Increased

-- B y   S i m o n e   M e i e r
-- 
2011-05-19T05:32:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-19/richemont-says-its-full-year-operating-profit-jumps-63-as-sales-increased.html
Cie. Financiere Richemont SA said
full-year operating profit rose 63 percent to 1.4 billion euros,
while sales jumped 33 percent to 6.89 billion euros.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Simone Meier at 
 smeier@bloomberg.net  